snippet.title: Jallooligans Kickstarter Video
snippet.description:
Crank the volume and watch the totally serious Kickstarter pitch for the Jallooligan's early access game "Crime is Sexy."
Then download the game here: http://jallooligans.itch.io/crime-is-sexy

Team:
Lauren Cruikshank
Jeff Mundee
Rebecca Goodine
Nicholas Polchies
Nathan Thompson
Chad Comeau
Jade Yhap

Made for the 2015 Jalloo game jam: http://jalloo.net/Jalloo15/default.html
